Python Projects

This repository contains four Python projects demonstrating automation, API usage, and working with external data.

 üìå Projects Included

1. LinkedIn Apply Bot
- Automates job applications on LinkedIn using Selenium.
- Demonstrates browser automation, element handling, and web scraping.

2. Flight Deals Tracker
- Uses external APIs and Sheety.
- Tracks flight prices and updates data dynamically.
- Sends alerts when flight prices drop.

3. Rain Alert App
Uses weather API to check rain forecast.
Sends SMS/notification if rain is expected.

4.Spotify Time Machine (Python, Flask, BeautifulSoup, Spotify API) 
Developed a Flask application that scrapes historical Billboard Hot 100 data using BeautifulSoup. 
Integrated the Spotify API to automatically search for matched tracks and generate custom playlists. 

